		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />lower case characters have been implemented, so here's a preliminary look at a cutscene with the newfangled standard font. <br /><br />ignore random Kalinka in tile data. that'll be removed of course.<br /><br /><img src="http://25.media.tumblr.com/b1406566209eb18785f384cb080ec0eb/tumblr_moznhpNE6x1rc7qlzo1_1280.png" alt="Image" /><br /><br />I'm mostly guessing at the exact character spacing based on the spacing I've seen in other games with this exact font. I'm pretty satisfied with it, with the exception of the p's and q's. The characters look out of place, and it almost makes me want to try to rewrite the dialogue again to avoid the use of either character. Maybe that's just because I've been staring at this font for the past few hours.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
